Package: climateBR
Type: Package
Title: Climate Data from INMET
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Kaio", "Bárbara", email = "kaio.rb@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Provides functions to download and import meteorological data 
    from Brazil's National Institute of Meteorology (INMET, <https://portal.inmet.gov.br>). 
    The package facilitates access to rainfall and other climate variables 
    recorded across hundreds of automatic weather stations throughout Brazil,
    covering the period from 2000 to the present.
